The opensource tivodecode is required to use the sample/useful
TiVo2Disk script.  You can find tivodecode at
http://tivodecode.sourceforge.net/

A unix environment is assumed for this script.  Tested under Linux and
OS X.

Credit where credit is due
--------------------------

This project redistributes, but does not modify, code from the
httpclient project maintained by NAKAMURA, Hiroshi.  You can find it
at http://dev.ctor.org/http-access2/

This project redistributes, but does not modify, code from the facets
ruby library, specifically Console::ProgressBar by Satoru Takabayashi.
You can find it at http://facets.rubyforge.org/
